aces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個名！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3e4e8b56bbca07b2717f9f6520fd024af879f7","tid":2120100,"uid":347008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f60706a26e9f80615dbee572022c8cc4b832445c","tid":2120100,"uid":71930,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:16:16.000Z","msg":"Poly: 唔好入poly 好閪<br />\nHku: 唔好入hku 好閪<br />\nCU: 唔好入CU 好閪<br />\n2020DSEers: 咁我要點<br />\nPoly hku cu: 咪撚入nursing<br />\n<br />\n講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"千！萬！不！要！入！理！大！護！理！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118503</a><br />\n<br />\n關於 Polyu Nursing placement 單野，我有野想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2119676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2119676</a><br />\n<br />\n各有各閪法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有辣有唔辣<br />\nPoly 嘅閪法自己入去睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5ca5988a8c69e6a42e6c98dca07bf0ebadba9e","tid":2120100,"uid":22046,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:38:58.000Z","msg":"行內印象 <br />\npoly sharp醒 hku離地 cu無特別 ou蠢/懶 東華地底泥<br />\n醫院school 快手,knowledge差d<br />\n<br />\n不過比我揀點都唔入school<br />\n有degree 要升都無咁煩"},{"pid":"3c6801634193791784e815c269f4889f78d7f76e","tid":2120100,"uid":71930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"而家睇 最唔閪咪CU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 唔係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db501bfb882fb919e98d45a5ee35bbe32c136464","tid":2120100,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:50:03.000Z","msg":"好奇一問<br />\n<br />\n邊個U都係出黎都係做RN, 職位又100%就業咁濟<br />\n就算講升都係5年後既事, 到時真係咁睇邊間大學?<br />\n唔同大學出黎真係咁大分別?"},{"pid":"ffdec4c7ebb307f1cf81549e9d77d23abd8cdb07","tid":2120100,"uid":214923,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"nursing有得揀嘅話 都係poly同CU比較好<br />\n兩間都有各自嘅優缺點<br />\n利申左先 CU nursing已grad <br />\n<br />\nCU嘅話有人覺得theory多d <br />\n我自己覺得就還可以<br />\n雖然school嘅高層係十分離地<br />\n但d tutor大部分都Ok 不過好嗰d聽講走左唔少<br />\n<br />\npracticum嘅時候 可能無poly嘅學生咁醒<br />\n始終year2先出ward 而且一開始都係鴨仔團<br />\nyear 4就算無tutor都幾個人一齊出<br />\n不過醒唔醒目都係睇人 肯比心機嘅總會好d<br />\n<br />\n奉勸一句 <br />\n諗清楚自己係咪真係有心做護士先啦<br />\n依份工真係唔好做㗎"}]}